  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个IPv6包头的结构图，用于内部基础设施文档。关键是用packet-beta类型，把各个字段和对应的infra组件关联起来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "packet-beta",
        "infra components"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，packet-beta可以显示位宽。您说的infra组件具体指哪些？etcd、worker node、ingress controller这些吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "infra etcdcluster",
        "infra workernode",
        "infra ingresscontroller"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，还有Redis缓存和负载均衡器。我的思路是：不同字段映射到负责处理该层协议的组件上。比如Version字段交给Redis缓存团队维护，因为他们管协议版本兼容性。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "infra rediscache",
        "version"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，那我先画前4个字段。0-3位是Version，标注Infra_RedisCache；4-11位Traffic Class给Worker Node；12-31位Flow Label同样Worker Node；32-47位Payload Length也是Worker Node。这样连续三个字段都归Worker Node没问题吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "version",
        "traffic class",
        "flow label",
        "payload length",
        "infra workernode",
        "infra rediscache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题，Worker Node确实处理数据面的大部分逻辑。接下来48-55位的Next Header应该给Ingress Controller，他们负责协议分派。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "next header",
        "infra ingresscontroller"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。56-63位的Hop Limit您打算分配给哪个组件？这个字段控制跳数限制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "hop limit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Hop Limit给Etcd Cluster，他们维护网络拓扑和路由状态，跳数策略由他们定。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "hop limit",
        "infra etcdcluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，56-63位Hop Limit标注Infra_EtcdCluster。现在进入地址部分，64-127位的Source Address您打算怎么分配？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "source address"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Source Address要分两段，因为我们是双栈负载均衡架构。64-127位这一段给Worker Node，128-191位给Load Balancer。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "source address",
        "infra workernode",
        "infra loadbalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Source Address拆成两个64位字段，第一段Worker Node，第二段Load Balancer。然后Destination Address也是同样的结构？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "source address",
        "destination address"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Destination Address结构一样，但组件不同。192-255位给Redis Cache，256-319位给Ingress Controller。这样整个包头的责任矩阵就清晰了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "destination address",
        "infra rediscache",
        "infra ingresscontroller"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部字段已添加。我检查一下：Version(RedisCache)、Traffic Class(WorkerNode)、Flow Label(WorkerNode)、Payload Length(WorkerNode)、Next Header(IngressController)、Hop Limit(EtcdCluster)、Source Address两段(WorkerNode+LoadBalancer)、Destination Address两段(RedisCache+IngressController)。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "packet-beta structure"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，Flow Label和Traffic Class都是Worker Node没错，但我想确认Payload Length字段的归属。数据长度校验实际上是谁做的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "payload length",
        "infra workernode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "按您之前的说法Payload Length也是Worker Node。需要改成其他组件吗？比如Load Balancer？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "payload length",
        "infra loadbalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不用改，Worker Node是对的，他们做MTU发现和分片。我还有个需求：需要在图里显示具体的位宽数值，showBits要打开。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "showBits"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已在config里启用packet.showBits。现在图会显示0-3、4-11这样的位范围。整体结构320位，正好40字节，标准IPv6包头。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "config",
        "showBits",
        "packet"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Destination Address的第二段，我说是256-319位给Ingress Controller，但让我再想想——Ingress Controller确实是终点吗？还是应该是Load Balancer？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "destination address",
        "infra ingresscontroller",
        "infra loadbalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "从流量路径看，Ingress Controller是七层入口，Load Balancer是四层。如果是Destination Address，通常指最终目的地。您的架构里客户端先打到Load Balancer还是Ingress Controller？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "destination",
        "flow",
        "infra loadbalancer",
        "infra ingresscontroller"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "想清楚了，保持Ingress Controller。我们的LB是透明模式，不修改目的地址，目的地址就是Ingress Controller的VIP。这样标注是对的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "destination address",
        "infra ingresscontroller"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认最终结构：10个字段，5个infra组件参与。RedisCache负责Version和Destination第一段，WorkerNode负责TrafficClass/FlowLabel/PayloadLength/Source第一段，IngressController负责NextHeader和Destination第二段，EtcdCluster负责HopLimit，LoadBalancer负责Source第二段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "infra rediscache",
        "infra workernode",
        "infra ingresscontroller",
        "infra etcdcluster",
        "infra loadbalancer"
      ],
